project_description: IDB pull of patient demographics
Processing of patient diagnosis, with an emphasis on Disease events
ID mapping
Patient insurance history
IDB pull of interventional radiology events
IDB pull of patient surgeries performed at MSKCC
IDB pull of radiation oncology events
Processing of anti-cancer mediations administered at MSKCC. Inferred treatment intervals and regimens.
Patient comorbidities derived from ICD billing codes, including Charlson Comorbidity and NCI Index calculations
Processing of radiology reports to break down into sections and create metadata
Identify Disease sites from Radiology reports using NLP
Identify disease progression (stable, worsening, progression)
Identify Smoking History of Genie BPC primary Lung Cancer patients (i.e. Current/Previous smoker, Never, or Unknown) using NLP and/or regex solution.
Processing of pathology reports to break down into sections and create metadata. Includes Regex of IHC and other histopathologic markers
Identify medications given outside of MSK, using NLP
Approximate the yost index (a measure of socioeconomic status) for all IMPACT patients, based on the patient address (census tract)

Identify primary breast cancer patients with local recurrence and/or metastatic disease using NLP/Medical Oncology notes. Approximate the local and/or metastatic recurrence date based on the first predicted metastatic note.
Identify biopsy vs. resection pathology reports using NLP and/or regex
Identify invasive vs. benign biopsy using NLP/pathology reports
Identify histology for resections
Identify histology for cancerous biopsies
Identify Her2, PDL1, ER, PR status of primary breast cancer patient samples (regex/python-based solution) on pathology notes.
Identify primary gi cancer patients with metastatic disease. Approximate the metastatic recurrence date for patients predicted metastatic.
Model overall survival using diverse set of clinicogenomic features
Extract/impute pack year smoking history value from medical oncology (Clindoc) notes
IDB pull of patient lab results
Ancestry profiling using genomic (MSK-IMPACT) sequencing
Data transformations required for pushing data to cbioportal
Data containing frequently acquired markers for calculating allostatic load, a measurement of biologic stress that can affect cancer outcomes.
Patient and sample summary data hosted on cBioPortal containing genomic information. Sourced from MPath and CVR.
Infomation on patient adverse events or toxicities related to anti-cancer medications
Identify disease-free status from radiology reports
